reviews.text:
Great Salvadoran food! The service A1!
Had a great breakfast, chesse,eggs,yuca,beans and more!
Pretty low key restaurant,closer to just a food stand really, inside Saraga grocery store. Ordered the Grilles chicken dinner and 2 tacos, 1 beef & 1...
Cheese pupusas are really good. The cabbage and tomato sauce on the side is tasty too. Definitely recommend. Price is very cheap too.
